Package: HydRochemistRy
Type: Package
Title: Package to analyze hydrochemical data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mike Wit
Maintainer: Mike Wit <m.r.j.wit@tudelft.nl> <mike.r.j.wit@gmail.com> 
Description: Function to analyze hydrochemical data, including:
    checking and validating lab results;
    calculating ionic balance;
    plotting piper diagrams;
    more to come in the future.
